{"tid":2362823,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"一鍵投訴練錦鴻法官","createTime":"2021-01-11T17:16:55.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-19T11:01:43.000Z","uid":364713,"like":124,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":84,"replies":[{"pid":"e9065c8a0691f46f8194ddb3c66213ecd6a7031d","tid":2362823,"uid":364713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T17:16:55.000Z","msg":"區域法官法官練錦鴻今日審案時，叫戴黃色口罩既律師同旁聽人士離席，嚴重損害被告利益同埋法庭審訊公正性，亦令人有觀感認為佢偏頗。<br />\n<br />\n投訴信已經準備好。有兩個版本，任君選擇。大家亦可以自己寫投訴信，寫出自己既投訴理據。<br />\n版本一 <a href=\"https://docdro.id/3BJ1f1N\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocdro.id%2F3BJ1f1N&d=bDhD0m8o4fsrNJ%2BdslRS%2BYlFrThteLnMWGuqQSPs63E%3D&h=3d6d0ae0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docdro.id/3BJ1f1N</a><br />\n版本二 <a href=\"https://docdro.id/N7wTPjK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocdro.id%2FN7wTPjK&d=bDhD0m8o4fsrNJ%2BdslRS%2BYlFrThteLnMWGuqQSPs63E%3D&h=81ffa78f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docdro.id/N7wTPjK</a><br />\n<br />\n所有投訴法官既文件必須郵寄，勞煩大家(1) 喺template既灰色地方輸入個人資料，(2) 印出嚟再簽名，(3) 然後郵寄。<br />\n<br />\n我之前寫咗幾封投訴信，投訴其他偏頗既法官，大家亦可列印然後寄出。<br />\n最後，希望大家多旁聽，多寫信俾牆內手足。撐手足，撐到底。<br />\n<br />\n立場新聞報導<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/court/%E6%B7%98%E5%A4%A7%E8%A1%9D%E7%AA%81-%E5%9B%9B%E7%94%B7%E8%AA%8D%E9%9D%9E%E6%B3%95%E9%9B%86%E7%B5%90-%E6%B3%95%E5%AE%98%E7%B7%B4%E9%8C%A6%E9%B4%BB%E8%B6%95%E6%88%B4%E9%BB%83%E5%8F%A3%E7%BD%A9%E5%BE%8B%E5%B8%AB%E9%9B%A2%E5%B8%AD-%E8%B3%AA%E7%96%91%E7%8F%BE%E5%A0%B4-%E9%BB%83%E8%83%8C%E5%BF%83-%E6%9A%B4%E5%8B%95/?fbclid=IwAR139mDnNG9rBngfqmFrhLIiVcIQ6uolr1FLzNwv6GYP3CPUerh5_CbQUOg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F%25E6%25B7%2598%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E8%25A1%259D%25E7%25AA%2581-%25E5%259B%259B%25E7%2594%25B7%25E8%25AA%258D%25E9%259D%259E%25E6%25B3%2595%25E9%259B%2586%25E7%25B5%2590-%25E6%25B3%2595%25E5%25AE%2598%25E7%25B7%25B4%25E9%258C%25A6%25E9%25B4%25BB%25E8%25B6%2595%25E6%2588%25B4%25E9%25BB%2583%25E5%258F%25A